## mnv1 Important Info

If you are on `mnv1` (for example, `hostname` returns `mnv1`), the main work folder is `~/Projects`. In chezmoi, this machine is identified as `work_mnv1`. It contains the main repos and worktrees used for development, and some worktrees have corresponding conda environments. If you have not already, read `~/.agent_files/work_mnv1/docs/workspace_setup.md` for the important machine-specific workspace details.
